<item>
            <title>[LU-15676] Interop sanity-sec test_47: Invalid cross-device link</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15676</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/09838ea8-8c85-4a92-ba12-775d8994ed12&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/09838ea8-8c85-4a92-ba12-775d8994ed12&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_47 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;rename from encrypted to unencrypted dir should succeed
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;interop testing between master and 2.14&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== sanity-sec test 47: encrypted file access semantics: rename/link ================================== 04:31:24 (1644381084)
10.240.24.91@tcp:/lustre /mnt/lustre lustre rw,flock,user_xattr,lazystatfs,encrypt 0 0
CMD: onyx-50vm1.onyx.whamcloud.com grep -c /mnt/lustre&apos; &apos; /proc/mounts
Stopping client onyx-50vm1.onyx.whamcloud.com /mnt/lustre (opts:)
CMD: onyx-50vm1.onyx.whamcloud.com lsof -t /mnt/lustre
CMD: onyx-50vm1.onyx.whamcloud.com umount  /mnt/lustre 2&amp;gt;&amp;amp;1
Starting client: onyx-50vm1.onyx.whamcloud.com:  -o user_xattr,flock,test_dummy_encryption onyx-50vm4@tcp:/lustre /mnt/lustre
CMD: onyx-50vm1.onyx.whamcloud.com mkdir -p /mnt/lustre
CMD: onyx-50vm1.onyx.whamcloud.com mount -t lustre -o user_xattr,flock,test_dummy_encryption onyx-50vm4@tcp:/lustre /mnt/lustre
1+0 records in
1+0 records out
524288 bytes (524 kB, 512 KiB) copied, 0.00318379 s, 165 MB/s
rename returned -1: Invalid cross-device link
ln: failed to create hard link &apos;/mnt/lustre/d47.sanity-sec/f47.sanity-sec&apos; =&amp;gt; &apos;/mnt/lustre/junk&apos;: Invalid cross-device link
rename returned 0: Success
rename returned -1: Invalid cross-device link
 sanity-sec test_47: @@@@@@ FAIL: rename from encrypted to unencrypted dir should succeed 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;






&lt;p&gt;VVVVVVV DO NOT REMOVE LINES BELOW, Added by Maloo for auto-association VVVVVVV&lt;br/&gt;
